page.title: 18Life Styles in West Enfield.
page.content: When my mum wakes me up I get up.This is normally around 7:30am.I get dressed immediately and when it's my turn in the bathroom I go in ,to wash.We work on a rota system.On school days I wear my school uniform but normally it is jeans and a T.shirt or jumper.I go downstairs to eat my breakfast which is normally cereal and sometimes a grapefruit.Then I make my packed lunch if it is a school day,and pack my bag.I leave for school at about 8:30am.At school the first lesson is normally maths or English except on Mondays and Wednesdays when we have silent reading.Our first break is at 10:30am and we have lunch at 12:00.We have Physical Education twice a week and art once.We have the computer once a week with eductional games.Our last break is at 2:30pm and we go home at quarter to four.
